{
  "stem": "24212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I became a member very early-- in the child category still-- member of the Czech sports club, swimming division.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I spent every possible hour in the summer-- didn't have winter pools at that time-- at the swimming pool, swimming, training, winning races-- never lost a race- and just socializing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a wonderful period of growing up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the winter, I had a different kind of a group, and we went skiing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in between, we had-- we went kayaking on the river.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And to see Czechoslovakia, which is called the land of the Yankees of Europe, was very sports-minded and helped young people do sports.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had all kinds of lower rates in-- not hotels.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What would we call-- the hostels for skiing and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were special trains that took our bicycles down the river, over weekends only.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went down by-- kayak or canoe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And coming back, again, we could put the kayak on the train, freight train, for peanuts really, and bicycle back home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this went on year by year, weekend by weekend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But mostly we knew the trails from hiking because that leads into our subject, you know, of smuggling people across the border, and all that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you have any particularly close friendships, either from the sporting groups or school?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had many, many good friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I mean good friends, not in the superficial sense, you know, you meet somebody and he's a friend.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean a friend who would take off his last shirt from his back or her back, and vice versa.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had many good friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And little by little, I'm losing them, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
